ion of the ergodic rate is derived for the algorithm,\nshowing that a practical digital combiner with two-stage analog combining also\nachieves the optimal scaling law. Simulation results validate the algorithm\nperformance and the derived ergodic rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Aug 2018 20:37:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Aug 2018 03:49:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
